Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次…世界大战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争的结果是 到2036年时全世界已经有57亿人丧生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而战争的契机就是…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个?这是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机器人吧?会变形什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是叔叔 果然认识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从α世界线来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这三周之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次 无数次的改变世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜牺牲了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才到达了这个β世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这一切成为徒劳…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像之前在广播馆被刺杀的科学家就叫这个名字哎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部伦太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说为了回避世界大战所需要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救在2010年7月28日死去的牧瀬红莉栖呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细情况我也不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我接到的任务只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救牧瀬红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:43.59,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且到达不受世界线收束范围影响的唯一的世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:46.32,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(685,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往命运石之门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:21.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(690,660)}境界面上的命运石之门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.31,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运石之门?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设立这个计划的 是未来的叔叔和父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现阶段一切都只是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你们两个的理论是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:41.63,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(665,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不存在命运石之门这条世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过即使如此我也还是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上会有一个美好未来在等待的这个未知可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果叔叔愿意和我一起去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就握住这只手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…真由喜虽然对刚才这番话一头雾水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫做红莉栖小姐的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对冈伦来说是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那冈伦不是该努力一下才对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得第三次世界大战之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冈伦的妄想太接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根本就没别的人能依靠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对未来的57亿人的性命没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搭乘上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐两个人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这可是出自我父亲之手的最棒杰作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手机留下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为可能会跟那边叔叔带的手机产生混淆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是时间机器?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然我已经搭乘它去过1975年以及2000年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过运行状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 燃料要吃紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 它也能从过去跳向未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 因为是时间机器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和那时的世界线不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去的是7月28日12点前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到达的地点是无法更改的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要是去的太早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会在广播馆引起骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会改变牧瀬红莉栖的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次坐的话 估计会有很严重的重力反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然会出现的东西 就像是时光碎片一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我胃液倒流了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免与这个时间点上的自己接触
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.53,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(859,660)}time paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那样会引起严重的时间悖论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离她被刺还有多久?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有大约20分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去设置时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔去保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我叔叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日 我看到红莉栖倒在血泊中的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和真由理一起参加了中钵博士的见面会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后听到了楼顶上发出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来 真由理等一下会去7楼乌帕的扭蛋机那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为了这个才叫我过来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个系列已经没剩多少了 但真由喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百元硬币用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 从里面的楼梯回到8楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金属的啊 金属乌帕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很稀有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 超级稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道我的名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖还…活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在哪里见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听我说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:20.95,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 位于8楼大厅的中钵博士见面会即将召开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:26.67,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 位于8楼大厅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器的基本构造如你们所见已经印在了发给大家的资料上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我就只说明一下基础理论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就计划书上来说 叔叔你应该要一直尾随牧瀬红莉栖才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 把她带去外面也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能确认杀死她的凶手跟原因的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来很有可能还是一样走向死亡的收束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真由理那时一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博～士!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊?这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的时间机器理论是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克尔黑洞 世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是约翰·提托…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久 红莉栖就将在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是在别的地方被刺了 然后再被搬到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这个可能性也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然接下来会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在看的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以红莉栖在每次世界线改变后都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 混账小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…希望您能看看这个 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是中钵博士?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸时隔七年联系了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了让我来见面会对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就成为了契机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 红莉栖的父亲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整理了脑海中浮现的理论 觉得没准真的能制造出时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听听爸爸的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这篇论文能被承认的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逐出学会的爸爸也能卷土重来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是被逐出去的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我看不惯他们 然后主动离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 只要爸爸你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以跟爸爸共同署名发表这篇论文
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为契机是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这篇论文会署上我一个人的名字然后发表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道爸爸你打算盗用我的论文吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为只有这种事您是绝对不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢说我盗用?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就这么优秀啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没道理孩子比父母还要优秀!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有你 我就能一直保持优秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们事先商量好了 想要搞砸我的见面会对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…保护红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 爸爸 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我指手画脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:13.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又明白些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感受 我的这份屈辱 我身处的地狱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红…红莉栖?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个笨蛋 真是和你们无比相衬的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 把你也牵扯进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是我父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到爸爸的认同 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…还不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了 杀了 杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦 你那满身的血是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 这不是叔叔的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀了…是我杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…杀了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔我知道你很痛苦 但还不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器还留有再一次回到过去的燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 就算再回去也一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:39.37,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(499,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正因为世界线收束范围的收束 红莉栖总会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冈伦的手机…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs54\be2\fr-12\an1\move(204,578,191,545,600,1900)\t(600,1900,1,\fs70)}看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中钵博士搭乘的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fr27\pos(653,581)\c&HB5B4B1&}中钵博士 逃亡俄罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然货物舱起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像仍然勉强在逃亡目的地的俄罗斯着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 真是得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠这个东西被金属探测器发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以论文没有被大火烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:16.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是真由喜的金属乌帕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还写着真由喜的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎 但是为什么在俄罗斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇论文就是一切的起因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此为契机 大国之间展开了激烈的时间机器开发竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要能统帅时间 就等于统帅了全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 最终发展成为了世界大战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事关57亿人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救红莉栖 然后改变世界线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真由理那时是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我怎么挣扎 结果都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖还是会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是一次失败…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我已经失败过几次…几十次了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时间之环究竟有多么不讲情理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有究竟会准备好多么残酷的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦不是那种会半途而废的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦绝对不是那种轻言放弃的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连真由喜无法跟奶奶说再见的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦也从未放弃 每天都会跟去墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才跟奶奶告别了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才变得这么有精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不能放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日那天 应该有收到一封影音邮件才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话应该可以看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是「拯救牧瀬红莉栖已经失败过一次」的现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瞒着没告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要经历过一次失败其实也在计划之内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让叔叔看到这段影像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是初次见面吧 15年前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冈伦啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然已经打开了这封邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味着你在拯救红莉栖这事上已经失败过一次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正是这份痛苦 给予了我执着的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能把它当做是「未曾发生过的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 这是相当于「事前准备」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来终于可以进入计划的正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:23.91,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(824,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救牧瀬红莉栖 并且进入命运石之门的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是把中钵博士带到俄罗斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于时间机器的论文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个世界上抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个 就是拯救牧瀬红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真能做到这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 想要回避牧瀬红莉栖的死亡并且改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.93,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(461,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点由于世界线收束范围的收束而成为了不可能的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就明说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救红莉栖是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是方法有误而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能改变既定的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让一开始你自己见到的事情变成「未曾发生过的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是变成「未曾发生过」的话 就会造成过去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一切都付诸东流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起你在α世界线所经历的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有短短三个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你应该还记得跟红莉栖一同度过的时间才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟红莉栖一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救真由理而牺牲了许多回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断挣扎的这份经历 应该还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让你那三个星期的世界线漂流白费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也绝对不能把它当做「未曾发生过的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为你到达过无数条世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以渴望拯救红莉栖的你才存在于那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把一切都奉献给时间机器开发的我才存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在所身处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为我们都渴望着拯救红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能到达的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 去欺骗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改变「红莉栖已死」这个过去的情况下救活她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让过去的自己将还活着的红莉栖「观测」为已死的红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话 就不会引发过去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话应该能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提 时间机器的型号是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C204型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首字母到底意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着我说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜（Cristina）…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:42.03,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(839,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外将目的地的世界线命名为命运石之门的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话应该也能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「并没有什么意义」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:59.46,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(625,660}Operation Skuld
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 对最终任务『掌管未来的女神』作战的概要进行说明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改变既定过去的情况下改变结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「浑身是血倒在地上的牧瀬红莉栖」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及「目睹了这一切的冈部伦太郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改变这些既定过去的条件下改变结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗最初的你!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗世界!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:22.78,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是到达命运石之门的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy Congroo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个是15年后的冈伦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音好低沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:49.90,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,660}Operation Skuld
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说『掌管未来的女神』?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说El Psy Congroo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都33岁了我还在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是中二病马力全开嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就做到给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:09.56,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说这就是命运石之门的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是疯狂的科学狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤凰院凶真!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗世界这种小事 不值一提!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 变回平时的那个冈伦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 真由喜还是更喜欢这样的冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我再说一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是疯狂的科学狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤凰院凶真!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界 是我的掌中之物!

Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:11.53,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去は離れて行き 未来は近づくの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:17.00,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,観測者はいつか 矛盾に気付く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:27.93,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神の創り出した世界は 完全なるもので 絶対の均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:34.81,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは折り重なる偶然 宇宙規模の奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:40.72,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守られてきた ゲート「規制」は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.00,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:47.60,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「0」が過去で 「1」が未来 「今」は何処にもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:52.55,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背く事の出来ぬロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.44,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:59.15,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並行する無数の線 選択は冒涜へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:04.49,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らの「存在」さえ疑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:10.94,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その目に映る景色は「収束」をする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:31.91,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二つの針が指す 時間の概念も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:37.46,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,観測者しだいで 歪みを見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:48.46,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神に与えられた英知は 必ず「果て」がある 絶対の領域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:54.96,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは愚かな故の偶然 招かれざる奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:23:00.89,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉ざされてきたゲート「規制」は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:01.99,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.68,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光速へと手を伸ばした 想い出のパルスが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:12.71,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛び込む不可思議なロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:13.57,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:19.20,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙がまだ隠し持った 秩序のない理論
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:24.35,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限と呼ばれた点と点が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:31.28,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正な力を借りて「再生」をする

Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:11.53,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去在在远离 未来正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:17.00,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测者总有一天会发现矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:27.93,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神所创造出来的世界 是完美之物 拥有绝对的均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:34.81,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是重叠在一起的偶然 引发出宇宙规模的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:40.72,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被守护着的 Gate 终于结束「限制」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.00,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:47.60,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「0」是过去 「1」是未来 「现在」则不曾存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:52.55,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法违背的逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.44,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:59.15,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并行排列的无数条线 选择终将变为冒渎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:04.49,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连我们的「存在」都会被质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:10.94,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼中映出的景色也终会「收束」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:31.91,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连两枚指针所指出的时间概念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:37.46,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会向观测者展现它的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:48.46,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由神所赋予的睿智 也终究会有「极限」 这是绝对的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:54.96,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是由于愚蠢的偶然 所招致而来的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:23:00.89,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被紧闭的Gate 终于结束「限制」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:01.99,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.68,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着光速伸出双手 回忆的脉冲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:12.71,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞入不可思议的逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:13.57,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
